lead_paragraph: Quarterback Russell Wilson had a hand in four touchdowns a week after throwing for five, and the Seahawks (7-5) improved their chances of playing in the postseason by dominating the Vikings (8-4).

headline.main: Seattle Routs Minnesota and Gains in Playoff Race
